graph TB
    subgraph "Training Operator Component"
        Controller[Training Operator<br/>Controller Manager]

        subgraph "Controllers"
            PyTorchCtrl[PyTorchJob Controller]
            TFJobCtrl[TFJob Controller]
            MPIJobCtrl[MPIJob Controller]
            XGBoostCtrl[XGBoostJob Controller]
            PaddleCtrl[PaddleJob Controller]
            JAXCtrl[JAXJob Controller]
        end

        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertMgr[Certificate Manager]
        Metrics[Metrics Exporter<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]

        Controller -->|manages| PyTorchCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| TFJobCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| MPIJobCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| XGBoostCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| PaddleCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| JAXCtrl

        CertMgr -->|provisions certs| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        PyTorchJobCR[PyTorchJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        TFJobCR[TFJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        MPIJobCR[MPIJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        XGBoostJobCR[XGBoostJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        PaddleJobCR[PaddleJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
        JAXJobCR[JAXJob CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        Pods[Training Pods<br/>Master + Workers]
        Services[ClusterIP Services<br/>Inter-pod comm]
        PodGroups[PodGroups<br/>Gang Scheduling]
        HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler<br/>Elastic Training]
        NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies<br/>Network Isolation]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| PyTorchJobCR
    User -->|creates| TFJobCR
    User -->|creates| MPIJobCR
    User -->|creates| XGBoostJobCR
    User -->|creates| PaddleJobCR
    User -->|creates| JAXJobCR

    PyTorchJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    TFJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    MPIJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    XGBoostJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    PaddleJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    JAXJobCR -->|validated by| Webhook

    PyTorchJobCR -->|watched by| PyTorchCtrl
    TFJobCR -->|watched by| TFJobCtrl
    MPIJobCR -->|watched by| MPIJobCtrl
    XGBoostJobCR -->|watched by| XGBoostCtrl
    PaddleJobCR -->|watched by| PaddleCtrl
    JAXJobCR -->|watched by| JAXCtrl

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    TFJobCtrl -->|creates| Pods
    MPIJobCtrl -->|creates| Pods

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Services
    TFJobCtrl -->|creates| Services

    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| PodGroups
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| HPA
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| NetworkPolicies

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>Gang Scheduling]
        SchedulerPlugins[Scheduler Plugins<br/>Alternative Gang Sched]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    end

    Controller -->|watches CRDs| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|creates resources| K8sAPI
    Webhook -->|receives validation| K8sAPI
    CertMgr -->|updates webhook config| K8sAPI

    PodGroups -.->|used by| Volcano
    PodGroups -.->|used by| SchedulerPlugins
    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integration"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Job Creation UI]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Post-training storage]
    end

    Dashboard -->|creates jobs via| K8sAPI
    Pods -.->|stores models| ModelRegistry

